It's supposed to.
 

00:28:51.529 --> 00:28:56.251
So despite all the best efforts
people make, things are not

00:28:56.251 --> 00:28:57.230
identical.
 

00:28:57.230 --> 00:29:01.368
But at the microscopic level of
electrons and protons,

00:29:01.368 --> 00:29:05.509
every proton anywhere in the
universe is identical.

00:29:05.509 --> 00:29:08.150
And they can be manufactured in
