00:34:02.479 --> 00:34:10.025
assumption called superposition
which says that if you want the

00:34:10.025 --> 00:34:14.396
force on 3 (should read 1),
when there is

00:34:14.396 --> 00:34:16.159
q_1 and
q_2,

00:34:16.159 --> 00:34:20.619
you find the force due to
