Here's the piece of paper.
 

00:35:42.639 --> 00:35:43.559
Here's the comb.
 

00:35:43.559 --> 00:35:47.559
The comb is positively charged.
 

00:35:47.559 --> 00:35:49.639
The paper is neutral.
 

00:35:49.639 --> 00:35:52.360
So anyway, there's nothing here
to be attracted to this one,

00:35:52.360 --> 00:35:56.838
but if you bring it close
enough, there are equal amount

00:35:56.838 --> 00:35:59.768
of positive and negative
