00:37:09.869 --> 00:37:11.639
They repel each other.
 

00:37:11.639 --> 00:37:12.989
They want to get out.
 

00:37:12.989 --> 00:37:14.179
Previously they couldn't get
out.

00:37:14.179 --> 00:37:17.365
They were stuck on the rod,
but now that you've made

00:37:17.365 --> 00:37:20.239
contact, some of them will jump
to that one.

00:37:20.239 --> 00:37:23.500
Then when you separate them,
you will have a ball with some

00:37:23.500 --> 00:37:25.793
plus charges,
and you will have a rod with

00:37:25.793 --> 00:37:31.880
more plus charges,
and they will repel each other.

00:37:31.880 --> 00:37:35.431
And finally I said if you take
two of these spheres,

00:37:35.431 --> 00:37:39.123
