electricity.

00:38:33.929 --> 00:38:37.516
But if you stand on a metallic
stool, on a metallic floor and

00:38:37.516 --> 00:38:41.041
put your hand in the socket,
you'll be part of an electrical

00:38:41.041 --> 00:38:41.760
circuit.
 

00:38:41.760 --> 00:38:44.436
The human body is a good
conductor of electricity,

00:38:44.436 --> 00:38:47.713
but what saves you is that it
cannot go from your feet to the

00:38:47.713 --> 00:38:48.260
floor.
 

