but in our course either we'll

00:38:52.501 --> 00:38:54.822
talk about insulators,
which don't conduct

00:38:54.822 --> 00:38:57.090
electricity, and perfect
conductors,

00:38:57.090 --> 00:38:59.920
which conduct electricity.
 

